Data --> Smallest unit , eg info in cell of excel 

MetaData --> data/info/details about data 

Database --> group of data stored , multiple rows & column exist.


Types_of_DB --> structured & unstructured

structured DB : r&c or tavular or excel formated data in DB. eg excel
Mysql
oracle
postgresql


unstructured DB : not in r&c -> pic,img,txt,ppt,word

